      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion that\u2019s ready for the road? This vehicle is a solid, functional choice that gets the job done! While it shows some honest character and typical wear from its travels, it remains a dependable ride that's perfect for daily commuting or weekend errands. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a well-maintained vehicle at a fantastic price!",
